1
00:00:12,638 --> 00:00:14,014
O'NEIL,
WE'VE GOT TO KEEP GOING.

2
00:00:14,139 --> 00:00:15,390
COME ON. GET UP.

3
00:00:15,516 --> 00:00:18,185
IT'S NO USE.
THEY'RE EVERYWHERE.

4
00:00:21,355 --> 00:00:22,857
CAPTAIN GAVE US
AN ORDER.

5
00:00:22,982 --> 00:00:24,859
WE'VE GOT TO FIND
SOME CLUE.

6
00:00:24,984 --> 00:00:26,861
IT'S NO USE, MR. SULU.

7
00:00:26,986 --> 00:00:28,445
LOOK.
THERE'S ONE OF THEM.

8
00:00:28,570 --> 00:00:30,656
THERE'S ANOTHER ONE.

9
00:00:32,157 --> 00:00:34,117
SCOUTING PARTY
TO ENTERPRISE--

10
00:00:34,242 --> 00:00:36,077
COME IN.

11
00:00:36,203 --> 00:00:37,287
WHAT IS IT, MR. SULU?

12
00:00:37,412 --> 00:00:39,289
CAPTAIN,
BEAM US UP QUICK.

13
00:00:39,414 --> 00:00:40,332
EMERGENCY.

14
00:00:40,457 --> 00:00:41,249
TRANSPORTER ROOM,

15
00:00:41,375 --> 00:00:43,502
LOCK ONTO SULU AND O'NEIL.

16
00:00:43,627 --> 00:00:45,253
BEAM UP IMMEDIATELY.

17
00:00:45,379 --> 00:00:46,254
WE'VE GOT TO MAKE
A RUN FOR IT.

18
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:49,132
WE CAN'T JUST
STAND HERE.

19
00:00:49,257 --> 00:00:50,509
MR. O'NEIL, STAND TIGHT.
THEY'LL BEAM US UP IN A MINUTE.

20
00:00:50,634 --> 00:00:52,427
RUN, I TELL YOU.
WE'VE GOT TO GET
OUT OF HERE.

21
00:00:52,553 --> 00:00:54,221
YOU KNOW WHAT
THEY'RE CAPABLE OF.

22
00:00:54,346 --> 00:00:55,931
O'NEIL!

23
00:01:02,897 --> 00:01:04,899
[ZAP]

24
00:01:24,793 --> 00:01:26,085
SULU, WHAT IS IT?

25
00:01:26,211 --> 00:01:27,546
WHERE'S LIEUTENANT O'NEIL?

26
00:01:29,798 --> 00:01:30,758
WHAT?

27
00:01:30,883 --> 00:01:32,217
WHO?

28
00:01:32,342 --> 00:01:34,261
LIEUTENANT O'NEIL--
WHERE IS HE?

29
00:01:34,386 --> 00:01:36,388
YOU...

30
00:01:36,513 --> 00:01:38,390
YOU'RE NOT
OF THE BODY.

31
00:01:38,515 --> 00:01:40,475
DR. McCOY.

32
00:01:40,601 --> 00:01:43,020
DR. McCOY,
TRANSPORTER ROOM,
QUICKLY.

33
00:01:43,144 --> 00:01:46,398
YOU, YOU DID IT.

34
00:01:47,733 --> 00:01:50,027
THEY KNEW WE WERE ARCHONS.

35
00:01:50,151 --> 00:01:52,696
THESE ARE THE CLOTHES
THEY WEAR, NOT THESE.

36
00:01:52,821 --> 00:01:55,824
SULU, TAKE IT EASY.

37
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:57,576
LANDRU.

38
00:01:59,578 --> 00:02:01,080
LANDRU.

39
00:02:02,039 --> 00:02:03,582
SIT DOWN.

40
00:02:08,420 --> 00:02:10,297
WHAT HAPPENED?

41
00:02:11,172 --> 00:02:14,175
THEY'RE WONDERFUL.

42
00:02:14,301 --> 00:02:17,054
THEY'RE
THE SWEETEST...

43
00:02:17,178 --> 00:02:20,307
FRIENDLIEST PEOPLE
IN THE UNIVERSE.

44
00:02:23,477 --> 00:02:26,271
IT'S PARADISE,
MY FRIEND.

45
00:02:27,022 --> 00:02:28,440
PARADISE.

46
00:02:28,565 --> 00:02:31,192
LIEUTENANT O'NEIL--
WHERE IS HE?

47
00:02:31,318 --> 00:02:32,861
PARADISE.

48
00:02:35,948 --> 00:02:38,575
PARADISE.

49
00:02:45,791 --> 00:02:49,753
SPACE--
THE FINAL FRONTIER.

50
00:02:49,878 --> 00:02:53,674
THESE ARE THE VOYAGES
OF THE STARSHIP ENTERPRISE.

51
00:02:53,799 --> 00:02:55,592
ITS FIVE-YEAR MISSION--

52
00:02:55,717 --> 00:02:58,679
TO EXPLORE
STRANGE NEW WORLDS...

53
00:02:58,804 --> 00:03:02,349
TO SEEK OUT NEW LIFE
AND NEW CIVILIZATIONS...

54
00:03:02,474 --> 00:03:06,603
TO BOLDLY GO WHERE
NO MAN HAS GONE BEFORE.

55
00:03:39,094 --> 00:03:41,013
CAPTAIN'S LOG.

56
00:03:41,138 --> 00:03:44,183
STARDATE 3156.2--

57
00:03:44,307 --> 00:03:46,643
WHILE ORBITING
PLANET BETA 3

58
00:03:46,768 --> 00:03:48,020
TRYING TO FIND SOME TRACE

59
00:03:48,145 --> 00:03:49,604
OF THE STARSHIP ARCHON

60
00:03:49,730 --> 00:03:51,773
THAT DISAPPEARED HERE
A HUNDRED YEARS AGO,

61
00:03:51,899 --> 00:03:54,359
A SEARCH PARTY CONSISTING
OF TWO ENTERPRISE OFFICERS

62
00:03:54,484 --> 00:03:56,778
WERE SENT
TO THE PLANET BELOW.

63
00:03:56,904 --> 00:03:58,780
MR. SULU HAS RETURNED,

64
00:03:58,906 --> 00:04:01,658
BUT IN A HIGHLY AGITATED
MENTAL STATE.

65
00:04:01,783 --> 00:04:04,161
HIS CONDITION REQUIRES
I BEAM DOWN

66
00:04:04,285 --> 00:04:06,830
WITH AN ADDITIONAL
SEARCH DETAIL.

67
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:12,836
MATERIALIZATION COMPLETED.
KIRK OUT.

68
00:04:23,847 --> 00:04:26,058
ODD.

69
00:04:26,850 --> 00:04:29,436
THE EXPRESSION
ON THAT MAN'S FACE,

70
00:04:29,561 --> 00:04:31,021
THE MINDLESSNESS,

71
00:04:31,146 --> 00:04:33,774
VACANT CONTENTMENT.

72
00:04:33,899 --> 00:04:35,525
LIKE SULU.

73
00:04:38,278 --> 00:04:41,406
IF EVERYBODY ON THIS PLANET
IS LIKE HIM...

74
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:45,202
LET'S GO.

75
00:04:53,543 --> 00:04:55,587
JOY TO YOU, FRIENDS.

76
00:04:55,712 --> 00:04:57,923
JOY TO YOU.

77
00:04:58,048 --> 00:05:00,842
YOU BE STRANGERS.

78
00:05:02,844 --> 00:05:04,721
COME FOR THE FESTIVAL,
ARE YOU?

79
00:05:04,846 --> 00:05:06,556
YES.

80
00:05:06,681 --> 00:05:08,809
GOT A PLACE
TO SLEEP IT OFF YET?

81
00:05:10,727 --> 00:05:12,729
GO AROUND TO REGER'S HOUSE.

82
00:05:12,854 --> 00:05:14,522
HE'S GOT ROOMS...

83
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:19,987
BUT YOU'LL HAVE TO HURRY.
IT'S ALMOST THE RED HOUR.

84
00:05:23,573 --> 00:05:26,201
THIS, UH, FESTIVAL,

85
00:05:26,326 --> 00:05:28,745
IT STARTS AT 6:00?

86
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:33,834
TULA,
THESE FOLKS COME
FOR THE FESTIVAL.

87
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:36,670
YOUR DADDY
CAN PUT THEM UP,
CAN'T HE?

88
00:05:40,548 --> 00:05:41,967
YOU'RE FROM THE VALLEY?

89
00:05:42,092 --> 00:05:44,970
WE'VE, UH,
JUST ARRIVED.

90
00:05:45,095 --> 00:05:47,889
MY FATHER WILL BE GLAD
TO PUT YOU UP, THOUGH.

91
00:05:50,391 --> 00:05:52,144
IT'S RIGHT OVER THERE.

92
00:05:52,269 --> 00:05:54,313
[CLOCK BELL TOLLS]

93
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:02,361
AAH!

94
00:06:11,121 --> 00:06:13,290
TULA, COME!

95
00:06:14,373 --> 00:06:16,126
[SHOUTING]

96
00:06:25,052 --> 00:06:27,846
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE!

97
00:06:52,411 --> 00:06:54,915
I'M SORRY TO BREAK
IN ON YOU LIKE THIS.

98
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,250
WE DIDN'T EXPECT
THAT KIND OF A WELCOME.

99
00:06:56,375 --> 00:06:58,960
WELCOME?
YOU ARE STRANGERS?

100
00:06:59,086 --> 00:07:00,170
YES, THAT'S RIGHT.

101
00:07:00,295 --> 00:07:02,756
WE'RE...FROM THE VALLEY.

102
00:07:02,881 --> 00:07:04,216
YOU CAME
FOR THE FESTIVAL?

103
00:07:04,341 --> 00:07:05,175
YES.

104
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,467
AND HOW
COME YOU HERE?

105
00:07:06,593 --> 00:07:07,761
ARE YOU REGER?

106
00:07:07,886 --> 00:07:09,512
YES.

107
00:07:09,637 --> 00:07:10,764
YOU HAVE A DAUGHTER
NAMED TULA?

108
00:07:10,889 --> 00:07:12,349
YES.

109
00:07:12,473 --> 00:07:15,394
WELL, YOU BETTER DO SOMETHING.
SHE'S OUTSIDE.

110
00:07:15,518 --> 00:07:17,312
I KNOW.

111
00:07:17,437 --> 00:07:19,273
IT'S FESTIVAL.

112
00:07:19,398 --> 00:07:21,275
IT'S THE WILL
OF LANDRU.

113
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:23,443
REGER, THESE
ARE YOUNG MEN.

114
00:07:23,568 --> 00:07:26,696
THEY ARE NOT
OLD ENOUGH
TO BE EXCUSED.

115
00:07:26,821 --> 00:07:28,115
THEY'RE VISITORS.

116
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,158
WELL, HAVE THEY
NO LAWGIVERS
IN THE VALLEY?

117
00:07:30,284 --> 00:07:32,535
WHY BE THEY NOT
AT THE FESTIVAL?

118
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:37,082
WE HEARD THAT YOU MIGHT
HAVE ROOMS FOR US.

119
00:07:37,207 --> 00:07:39,667
THERE.
YOU SEE, HACOM?

120
00:07:39,793 --> 00:07:41,962
THEY'VE MERELY COME
LOOKING FOR A PLACE
TO REST AFTERWARDS.

121
00:07:42,087 --> 00:07:44,256
THE RED HOUR
HAS ALREADY STRUCK.

122
00:07:44,381 --> 00:07:46,383
HACOM, THESE BE STRANGERS.

123
00:07:46,507 --> 00:07:48,468
THE VALLEY
HAS DIFFERENT WAYS.

124
00:07:48,593 --> 00:07:51,054
DO YOU SAY
THAT LANDRU
IS NOT EVERYWHERE?

125
00:07:51,179 --> 00:07:52,639
NO, OF COURSE NOT.

126
00:07:52,764 --> 00:07:55,475
IT'S SIMPLY THAT THEY
MAY HAVE DIFFERENT WAYS.

127
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,102
THEY'VE COME LOOKING
FOR SHELTER.

128
00:07:57,227 --> 00:07:58,937
CAN I TURN THEM AWAY?

129
00:07:59,062 --> 00:08:00,605
COME, PLEASE.

130
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:06,403
BUT THE GIRL, OUT THERE?

131
00:08:06,527 --> 00:08:08,196
SHE IS IN FESTIVAL,

132
00:08:08,322 --> 00:08:10,198
AS YOU SHOULD BE.

133
00:08:11,325 --> 00:08:13,201
COME, PLEASE. HURRY.

134
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:18,581
THE LAWGIVERS
SHOULD KNOW.

135
00:08:18,706 --> 00:08:20,583
SURELY, HACOM,
THEY ALREADY KNOW.

136
00:08:20,708 --> 00:08:22,210
ARE THEY NOT
INFALLIBLE?

137
00:08:22,336 --> 00:08:23,211
YOU MOCK THEM!

138
00:08:23,337 --> 00:08:25,380
YOU MOCK
THE LAWGIVERS.

139
00:08:25,505 --> 00:08:28,216
THAT THE STRANGERS
ARE NOT OF THE BODY,

140
00:08:28,342 --> 00:08:29,801
YOU WILL SEE.

141
00:08:29,926 --> 00:08:31,511
BUT, HACOM...

142
00:08:41,938 --> 00:08:44,607
YOU CAN RETURN HERE
AT THE CLOSE OF THE FESTIVAL.

143
00:08:44,732 --> 00:08:46,943
IT'S QUIET.
YOU'LL HAVE NEED OF REST.

144
00:08:47,068 --> 00:08:48,987
WE HAVE NO PLANS TO
ATTEND THE FESTIVAL,
SIR.

145
00:08:49,112 --> 00:08:51,781
[CROWD SHOUTING
AND GLASS BREAKING]

146
00:08:51,906 --> 00:08:53,908
THE HOUR HAS STRUCK.

147
00:08:54,034 --> 00:08:55,743
YOU CAN HEAR.

148
00:08:55,869 --> 00:08:59,206
I'D LIKE TO HEAR MORE ABOUT
THIS FESTIVAL...AND LANDRU.

149
00:09:03,502 --> 00:09:05,212
LANDRU?

150
00:09:05,337 --> 00:09:06,921
YOU ASK...

151
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:13,594
WELL, YOU'RE STRANGE.

152
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:16,431
YOU SCORN FESTIVAL?

153
00:09:16,973 --> 00:09:19,309
ARE YOU...

154
00:09:19,434 --> 00:09:21,436
ARE YOU...

155
00:09:21,561 --> 00:09:23,563
WHAT ABOUT LANDRU?

156
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:44,584
FESTIVAL!

157
00:09:44,709 --> 00:09:46,794
FESTIVAL!

158
00:09:56,346 --> 00:09:58,598
LANDRU.

159
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,727
MY GUESS IS
WE HAVE UNTIL MORNING.

160
00:10:02,852 --> 00:10:04,604
LET'S PUT THE TIME
TO GOOD USE.

161
00:10:04,729 --> 00:10:05,480
DOCTOR,
DO ATMOSPHERIC READINGS

162
00:10:05,646 --> 00:10:07,482
TO DETERMINE WHETHER
THERE'S ANYTHING

163
00:10:07,607 --> 00:10:09,234
IN THE AIR TO ACCOUNT
FOR ALL THIS.

164
00:10:09,359 --> 00:10:10,818
MR. LINDSTROM, CORRELATE
ALL THAT YOU'VE SEEN

165
00:10:10,944 --> 00:10:14,364
WITH ANY OTHER SOCIOLOGICAL
PARALLELS, IF ANY.

166
00:10:14,489 --> 00:10:16,074
MR. SPOCK...

167
00:10:17,867 --> 00:10:20,579
YOU AND I HAVE
SOME SERIOUS
THINKING TO DO.

168
00:10:20,703 --> 00:10:22,581
WHEN WE LEAVE HERE
TOMORROW MORNING,

169
00:10:22,705 --> 00:10:25,208
I WANT TO HAVE
A PLAN OF ACTION.

170
00:10:51,859 --> 00:10:53,903
[BELL TOLLING]

171
00:11:08,876 --> 00:11:12,422
SPOCK. SPOCK. LINDSTROM.

172
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,592
DOC.

173
00:11:15,716 --> 00:11:17,844
[WOMAN SCREAMING]

174
00:11:23,016 --> 00:11:24,767
NO. NOW IT'S OVER.

175
00:11:24,892 --> 00:11:27,270
NO, NO, IT'S ALL OVER NOW.

176
00:11:27,395 --> 00:11:29,648
IT'S ALL OVER NOW, TULA.

177
00:11:29,814 --> 00:11:31,525
THAT'S ALL RIGHT. QUIET.

178
00:11:33,067 --> 00:11:34,486
EXCUSE ME.
COME ON.

179
00:11:34,611 --> 00:11:36,488
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

180
00:11:36,613 --> 00:11:38,865
IT'S ALL OVER.

181
00:11:38,990 --> 00:11:40,450
HE'LL GIVE HER A SHOT.

182
00:11:40,575 --> 00:11:42,910
IT'LL CALM HER DOWN.
TRUST US.

183
00:11:43,036 --> 00:11:45,163
YOU DIDN'T EVEN TRY
TO BRING HER BACK.

184
00:11:45,288 --> 00:11:47,582
WHAT KIND OF FATHER
ARE YOU?

185
00:11:47,706 --> 00:11:49,792
IT'S LANDRU'S WILL.

186
00:11:49,917 --> 00:11:52,587
WHAT ABOUT LANDRU?
WHO IS HE?

187
00:11:52,711 --> 00:11:54,130
IT IS TRUE THEN.

188
00:11:54,255 --> 00:11:56,591
YOU DID NOT ATTEND
THE FESTIVAL
LAST NIGHT.

189
00:11:56,715 --> 00:11:58,510
NO.

190
00:11:58,635 --> 00:12:00,970
THEN YOU'RE NOT
OF THE BODY.

191
00:12:01,095 --> 00:12:03,223
YOU COULDN'T BE.

192
00:12:08,102 --> 00:12:10,397
SHE'S ASLEEP.

193
00:12:11,690 --> 00:12:13,525
ARE YOU...

194
00:12:16,653 --> 00:12:20,365
ARE YOU ARCHONS?

195
00:12:21,157 --> 00:12:23,284
WHAT IF WE ARE?

196
00:12:23,410 --> 00:12:25,995
IT WAS SAID
MORE WOULD FOLLOW.

197
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,581
IF YOU ARE INDEED--

198
00:12:27,706 --> 00:12:29,290
WE MUST HIDE THEM.
QUICKLY. THE LAWGIVERS.

199
00:12:29,416 --> 00:12:31,585
WE CAN TAKE CARE
OF OURSELVES.

200
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:33,461
LANDRU WILL KNOW.
HE WILL COME.

201
00:12:38,132 --> 00:12:39,842
HE IS THE ONE.

202
00:12:39,967 --> 00:12:42,596
HE MOCKED THE LAWGIVERS.
I HEARD HIM.

203
00:12:42,721 --> 00:12:44,681
NO, HACOM.
IT WAS A JEST.

204
00:12:44,805 --> 00:12:46,391
THE OTHERS,
THEY WERE HERE,

205
00:12:46,516 --> 00:12:48,309
BUT THEY SCORNED
THE FESTIVAL.

206
00:12:48,435 --> 00:12:49,686
I SAW IT.

207
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:52,939
TAMAR, STAND CLEAR.

208
00:12:56,693 --> 00:12:59,153
I HEAR...

209
00:12:59,279 --> 00:13:03,408
AND OBEY THE VOICE
OF LANDRU.

210
00:13:17,338 --> 00:13:20,634
YOU ATTACKED
THE BODY.

211
00:13:22,843 --> 00:13:27,223
YOU HAVE
HEARD THE WORD
AND DISOBEYED.

212
00:13:27,348 --> 00:13:29,267
YOU WILL BE
ABSORBED.

213
00:13:29,392 --> 00:13:31,394
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
ABSORBED?

214
00:13:31,519 --> 00:13:34,272
THERE. YOU SEE?
NOT OF THE BODY.

215
00:13:34,397 --> 00:13:38,568
YOU WILL BE
ABSORBED.

216
00:13:38,693 --> 00:13:41,028
THE GOOD IS ALL.

217
00:13:41,154 --> 00:13:44,991
LANDRU
IS GENTLE.

218
00:13:45,116 --> 00:13:47,535
YOU WILL COME.

219
00:13:56,169 --> 00:13:58,713
WE'RE NOT GOING
ANYWHERE.

220
00:13:58,837 --> 00:14:00,965
IT IS THE LAW.

221
00:14:01,090 --> 00:14:02,801
YOU MUST COME.

222
00:14:02,925 --> 00:14:05,303
I SAID WE'RE NOT
GOING ANYWHERE.

223
00:14:11,643 --> 00:14:13,770
EVIDENTLY THEY'RE NOT
PREPARED TO DEAL

224
00:14:13,894 --> 00:14:16,356
WITH OUTRIGHT DISOBEDIENCE.
HOW DID YOU KNOW?

225
00:14:16,481 --> 00:14:18,483
EVERYTHING WE'VE
SEEN HERE SO FAR

226
00:14:18,608 --> 00:14:21,736
SEEMS
TO INDICATE SOME
SORT OF COMPULSIVE,

227
00:14:21,861 --> 00:14:23,237
INVOLUNTARY STIMULUS
TO ACTION.

228
00:14:23,363 --> 00:14:26,616
YOUR ANALYSIS SEEMS LOGICAL.

229
00:14:33,039 --> 00:14:38,378
IT IS CLEAR
THAT YOU SIMPLY
DID NOT UNDERSTAND.

230
00:14:38,503 --> 00:14:40,547
I WILL REPHRASE.

231
00:14:40,672 --> 00:14:43,132
YOU ARE ORDERED
TO ACCOMPANY US

232
00:14:43,257 --> 00:14:45,552
TO THE ABSORPTION
CHAMBERS.

233
00:14:50,515 --> 00:14:52,350
WHY DID YOU KILL THAT MAN?

234
00:14:52,475 --> 00:14:54,018
OUT OF ORDER.

235
00:14:54,143 --> 00:14:57,355
YOU WILL OBEY.

236
00:14:57,480 --> 00:15:00,274
IT IS THE WORD
OF LANDRU.

237
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:03,027
YOU TELL LANDRU

238
00:15:03,152 --> 00:15:05,321
THAT WE'LL COME
IN OUR OWN TIME

239
00:15:05,446 --> 00:15:08,032
AND THAT WE'LL SPEAK
TO HIM.

240
00:15:12,286 --> 00:15:14,455
YOU CANNOT.

241
00:15:14,581 --> 00:15:18,752
IT IS LANDRU.

242
00:15:18,877 --> 00:15:20,044
LANDRU.

243
00:15:21,087 --> 00:15:23,339
FASCINATING.

244
00:15:23,464 --> 00:15:25,675
THIS IS MERELY
A HOLLOW TUBE, CAPTAIN.

245
00:15:27,134 --> 00:15:29,387
NO MECHANISM.

246
00:15:30,847 --> 00:15:33,182
THEY'RE COMMUNING.
WE HAVE TIME. COME WITH ME.

247
00:15:33,307 --> 00:15:34,267
WHERE TO?

248
00:15:34,392 --> 00:15:35,560
TO A PLACE I KNOW.
YOU'LL BE SAFE THERE.

249
00:15:35,685 --> 00:15:38,271
BUT WE MUST HURRY.
LANDRU WILL COME.

250
00:16:03,254 --> 00:16:06,340
QUITE A FESTIVAL
THEY HAD.

251
00:16:06,466 --> 00:16:07,341
PEACE.

252
00:16:07,467 --> 00:16:09,969
WHAT DO YOU MAKE
OF ALL THIS?

253
00:16:10,094 --> 00:16:11,763
TOTALLY ILLOGICAL.

254
00:16:11,888 --> 00:16:13,222
YESTERDAY WITHOUT APPARENT
CAUSE OR REASON,

255
00:16:13,347 --> 00:16:15,558
THEY WROUGHT TOTAL HAVOC,

256
00:16:15,683 --> 00:16:17,226
YET TODAY, NOW--

257
00:16:17,351 --> 00:16:18,645
NOW THEY'RE BACK
TO NORMAL.

258
00:16:21,648 --> 00:16:22,941
MORNING, FRIENDS.

259
00:16:23,065 --> 00:16:24,651
GOOD MORNING, BILAR.

260
00:16:24,776 --> 00:16:26,235
YOUR DAUGHTER--
THAT'S THE MAN!

261
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:28,154
NO, IT WASN'T BILAR.
IT WAS LANDRU.

262
00:16:28,279 --> 00:16:30,573
LET'S HURRY.
WE HAVEN'T MUCH TIME.

263
00:16:37,163 --> 00:16:38,539
IT'S TOO LATE. LOOK.

264
00:16:41,501 --> 00:16:42,543
WHAT IS IT?

265
00:16:44,170 --> 00:16:46,923
LANDRU--
HE'S SUMMONING THE BODY.

266
00:16:47,047 --> 00:16:49,801
TELEPATHY, CAPTAIN.

267
00:16:55,556 --> 00:16:58,601
PHASERS ON STUN.

268
00:17:00,186 --> 00:17:02,563
WHICH WAY, REGER?

269
00:17:02,689 --> 00:17:04,941
PERHAPS THROUGH THERE,
BUT LANDRU...

270
00:17:05,065 --> 00:17:06,317
WE'LL HANDLE LANDRU.

271
00:17:06,442 --> 00:17:07,610
JUST GET US
OUT OF THIS.

272
00:17:20,957 --> 00:17:23,083
I DON'T WANT
TO HURT THEM.
WARN THEM BACK.

273
00:17:23,209 --> 00:17:25,336
THEY'RE IN THE BODY.
IT'S LANDRU.

274
00:17:25,461 --> 00:17:28,381
PHASERS ON STUN,
WIDE FIELD. FIRE.

275
00:17:38,975 --> 00:17:41,019
FIRE.

276
00:17:49,276 --> 00:17:50,528
SECURITY.

277
00:17:50,653 --> 00:17:51,612
CAPTAIN.

278
00:17:53,364 --> 00:17:56,367
LIEUTENANT O'NEIL.
HE'S ONE OF OUR MEN.

279
00:17:56,492 --> 00:17:58,703
NOT ANYMORE.
HE'S BEEN ABSORBED.

280
00:17:58,828 --> 00:17:59,996
BRING HIM ALONG.

281
00:18:00,120 --> 00:18:01,748
BUT I TELL YOU,
HE'S ONE OF THEM.

282
00:18:01,873 --> 00:18:03,541
WHEN HE WAKES, LANDRU
WILL FIND US THROUGH HIM.

283
00:18:03,666 --> 00:18:05,543
LEAVE HIM THERE.
HE'S OUR ENEMY.
HE'S BEEN ABSORBED.

284
00:18:05,668 --> 00:18:06,293
CAPTAIN, NOW THAT WE'VE
GOT LIEUTENANT O'NEIL,

285
00:18:06,419 --> 00:18:07,837
LET'S BEAM UP
OUT OF HERE.

286
00:18:07,962 --> 00:18:09,923
WE STILL DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S HAPPENED
TO THE ARCHONS.

287
00:18:10,048 --> 00:18:12,008
WHICH WAY?
BRING HIM ALONG.

288
00:18:50,046 --> 00:18:51,380
PUT HIM OVER THERE.

289
00:18:51,505 --> 00:18:53,716
A LIGHTING PANEL.

290
00:18:53,841 --> 00:18:56,218
AMAZING
IN THIS CULTURE.

291
00:19:00,389 --> 00:19:02,016
COMES FROM A TIME
BEFORE LANDRU.

292
00:19:02,141 --> 00:19:04,310
BEFORE LANDRU?
HOW LONG AGO WAS THAT?

293
00:19:04,435 --> 00:19:07,354
NOBODY KNOWS
POSITIVELY.

294
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:10,024
SOME SAY AS LONG AGO
AS 6,000 YEARS.

295
00:19:10,149 --> 00:19:11,442
CAPTAIN, IT TOOK
A VERY ADVANCED TECHNOLOGY

296
00:19:11,567 --> 00:19:13,569
TO CONSTRUCT A DEVICE
LIKE THIS--

297
00:19:13,694 --> 00:19:15,154
INCONSISTENT
WITH THIS ENVIRONMENT--

298
00:19:15,279 --> 00:19:17,615
BUT NOT INCONSISTENT
WITH WHAT WE'VE SEEN.
SECURITY.

299
00:19:19,450 --> 00:19:23,121
THOSE STAFFS,
HOLLOW TUBES--

300
00:19:23,245 --> 00:19:26,206
ANTENNAE, SOME SORT
OF BROADCAST POWER.

301
00:19:26,332 --> 00:19:28,126
WHAT IS IT, MR. SPOCK?

302
00:19:28,250 --> 00:19:30,128
MOSTLY STRONG
POWER GENERATIONS, CAPTAIN,

303
00:19:30,252 --> 00:19:33,047
NEAR HERE, BUT RADIATING
IN ALL DIRECTIONS.

304
00:19:33,172 --> 00:19:34,381
HE'LL BE COMING AROUND
SOON, CAPTAIN.

305
00:19:34,507 --> 00:19:37,635
HE MUST NOT.
HE'S BEEN ABSORBED.

306
00:19:39,512 --> 00:19:42,015
ABSORBED?

307
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:43,766
THE BODY ABSORBS
ITS ENEMIES.

308
00:19:43,891 --> 00:19:45,392
IT ONLY KILLS
WHEN IT HAS TO.

309
00:19:45,518 --> 00:19:47,561
WHEN THE FIRST
ARCHONS CAME,

310
00:19:47,687 --> 00:19:49,229
THEY WERE FREE,
OUT OF CONTROL,

311
00:19:49,355 --> 00:19:51,398
OPPOSING THE WILL
OF LANDRU.

312
00:19:51,524 --> 00:19:53,317
MANY WERE KILLED,
MANY MORE WERE ABSORBED.

313
00:19:53,442 --> 00:19:55,319
WHEN HE REGAINS
CONSCIOUSNESS,

314
00:19:55,444 --> 00:19:57,113
LANDRU WILL FIND US
THROUGH HIM,

315
00:19:57,237 --> 00:19:58,447
AND IF
THE OTHERS COME--

316
00:19:58,572 --> 00:20:00,533
WHAT OTHERS?

317
00:20:00,658 --> 00:20:04,162
THOSE LIKE YOU AND ME,
WHO RESIST LANDRU.

318
00:20:04,286 --> 00:20:05,579
AN UNDERGROUND?

319
00:20:05,705 --> 00:20:08,166
HOW ARE YOU ORGANIZED?

320
00:20:12,294 --> 00:20:13,754
IN THREES--

321
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:15,255
MYSELF,

322
00:20:15,381 --> 00:20:17,175
TAMAR, WHO'S DEAD NOW,

323
00:20:17,299 --> 00:20:18,217
AND ONE OTHER.

324
00:20:18,342 --> 00:20:18,968
WHO?

325
00:20:19,093 --> 00:20:21,095
I DON'T KNOW.

326
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:24,223
TAMAR WAS MY CONTACT.

327
00:20:24,348 --> 00:20:27,060
GIVE ME
A DECISION, CAPTAIN.
HE'S COMING OUT OF IT.

328
00:20:28,895 --> 00:20:30,813
HE MUST NOT
REGAIN CONSCIOUSNESS.

329
00:20:30,938 --> 00:20:33,024
HE'LL DESTROY US ALL.
HE'S OF THE BODY.

330
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:38,029
GIVE HIM A SHOT.

331
00:20:38,154 --> 00:20:40,322
KEEP HIM ASLEEP.

332
00:20:40,447 --> 00:20:41,615
REGER...

333
00:20:44,660 --> 00:20:47,163
I WANT SOME ANSWERS.

334
00:20:50,166 --> 00:20:52,043
THIS UNDERGROUND--

335
00:20:52,168 --> 00:20:53,961
IF LANDRU'S
SO POWERFUL,

336
00:20:54,087 --> 00:20:55,337
HOW DO YOU SURVIVE?

337
00:20:55,462 --> 00:20:57,339
I DON'T KNOW, CAPTAIN.

338
00:20:57,464 --> 00:21:00,176
SOME OF US ESCAPED
THE DIRECTIVES.

339
00:21:00,300 --> 00:21:02,553
NOT MANY, BUT A FEW.

340
00:21:02,678 --> 00:21:04,931
IT WAS THAT WAY
WHEN THE FIRST ARCHONS CAME.

341
00:21:05,056 --> 00:21:08,559
THE ARCHONS...
TELL ME ABOUT THEM.

342
00:21:08,684 --> 00:21:10,561
THEY HAD INVADED THE BODY,

343
00:21:10,686 --> 00:21:13,272
BUT THEY RESISTED
THE WILL OF LANDRU.

344
00:21:13,397 --> 00:21:17,026
YOU SEE, LANDRU
HAD PULLED THEM DOWN
FROM THE SKIES.

345
00:21:17,151 --> 00:21:19,319
PULLED THEM DOWN
FROM THE SKIES?
A STARSHIP?

346
00:21:19,445 --> 00:21:22,531
MR. SPOCK, THOSE
POWER READINGS YOU
TOOK, ARE THEY...

347
00:21:22,656 --> 00:21:25,576
POWERFUL ENOUGH TO DESTROY
A STARSHIP? AFFIRMATIVE.

348
00:21:27,828 --> 00:21:30,998
KIRK TO ENTERPRISE,
COME IN.

349
00:21:31,124 --> 00:21:32,416
CAPTAIN,
WE'RE UNDER ATTACK.

350
00:21:32,541 --> 00:21:34,210
THERE ARE HEAT BEAMS
OF SOME KIND

351
00:21:34,334 --> 00:21:35,962
COMING UP
FROM THE PLANET'S
SURFACE.

352
00:21:36,087 --> 00:21:37,130
STATUS REPORT.

353
00:21:37,255 --> 00:21:38,214
OUR SHIELDS
ARE HOLDING,

354
00:21:38,338 --> 00:21:39,673
BUT THEY'RE TAKING
ALL OUR POWER.

355
00:21:39,799 --> 00:21:41,801
IF WE TRY TO WARP
OUT OR EVEN MOVE
ON IMPULSE ENGINES,

356
00:21:41,926 --> 00:21:43,469
WE'LL LOSE
OUR SHIELDS,

357
00:21:43,594 --> 00:21:44,720
AND WE'LL BURN UP
LIKE A CINDER.

358
00:21:44,845 --> 00:21:45,972
ORBIT CONDITION.

359
00:21:46,097 --> 00:21:47,807
CHECKING.

360
00:21:54,605 --> 00:21:55,606
WE'RE GOING DOWN,
CAPTAIN.

361
00:21:55,731 --> 00:21:57,524
UNLESS WE CAN GET
THOSE BEAMS OFF US

362
00:21:57,650 --> 00:21:58,692
SO WE CAN USE
OUR ENGINES,

363
00:21:58,818 --> 00:22:01,862
WE'RE DUE TO HIT
ATMOSPHERE IN LESS
THAN 12 HOURS.

364
00:22:01,988 --> 00:22:03,530
KEEP YOUR SHIELD UP.

365
00:22:03,656 --> 00:22:05,199
DO EVERYTHING YOU CAN
TO MAINTAIN ORBIT.

366
00:22:05,324 --> 00:22:07,367
WE'LL TRY AND LOCATE
THE SOURCE OF THE BEAM

367
00:22:07,493 --> 00:22:08,661
AND STOP IT HERE.

368
00:22:08,786 --> 00:22:10,121
IMPOSSIBLE TO BREAK
AWAY. I'VE TRIED

369
00:22:10,246 --> 00:22:11,622
THE EMERGENCY
BYPASS CIRCUITS,

370
00:22:11,747 --> 00:22:12,832
BUT THEY HAVEN'T
BEEN EFFECTIVE.

371
00:22:12,957 --> 00:22:15,168
[STATIC]

372
00:22:16,252 --> 00:22:18,587
[SPOCK]
CAPTAIN.

373
00:22:19,630 --> 00:22:20,923
WHAT IS IT?

374
00:22:21,048 --> 00:22:22,424
SENSOR BEAMS,
VERY STRONG.

375
00:22:22,549 --> 00:22:25,343
WE'RE BEING PROBED
IN THIS DIRECTION.

376
00:22:25,469 --> 00:22:26,553
LANDRU.

377
00:22:26,679 --> 00:22:28,055
BLOCK THEM OUT.

378
00:22:28,181 --> 00:22:30,183
TOO STRONG, CAPTAIN.
CAN'T BE BLOCKED.

379
00:22:30,308 --> 00:22:31,558
[WHIRRING SOUNDS]

380
00:22:31,684 --> 00:22:33,811
OOH...

381
00:22:44,864 --> 00:22:48,366
I AM LANDRU.

382
00:22:52,288 --> 00:22:53,956
PROJECTION, CAPTAIN.

383
00:22:54,081 --> 00:22:55,958
UNREAL.

384
00:22:56,083 --> 00:22:58,336
BUT BEAUTIFUL, MR. SPOCK,
WITH NO APPARATUS AT THIS END.

385
00:22:58,460 --> 00:23:02,173
YOU HAVE COME
AS DESTROYERS.

386
00:23:02,298 --> 00:23:04,967
YOU BRING AN INFECTION.

387
00:23:05,092 --> 00:23:07,345
YOU ARE HOLDING MY SHIP.

388
00:23:07,469 --> 00:23:08,554
I DEMAND
THAT YOU RELEASE IT.

389
00:23:08,679 --> 00:23:12,390
YOU HAVE COME TO A WORLD
WITHOUT HATE,

390
00:23:12,516 --> 00:23:14,392
WITHOUT FEAR,

391
00:23:14,518 --> 00:23:16,394
WITHOUT CONFLICT...

392
00:23:17,437 --> 00:23:18,981
NO WAR...

393
00:23:19,106 --> 00:23:21,525
NO DISEASE...

394
00:23:21,650 --> 00:23:23,944
NO CRIME...

395
00:23:24,070 --> 00:23:26,572
NONE OF THE ANCIENT EVILS.

396
00:23:28,032 --> 00:23:33,411
LANDRU
SEEKS TRANQUILITY...

397
00:23:33,537 --> 00:23:34,747
PEACE FOR ALL...

398
00:23:34,872 --> 00:23:37,166
THE UNIVERSAL GOOD.

399
00:23:37,291 --> 00:23:38,751
WE MEAN YOU NO HARM.

400
00:23:38,876 --> 00:23:40,460
OURS IS A MISSION
OF PEACE AND GOOD WILL.

401
00:23:40,586 --> 00:23:44,382
THE GOOD MUST TRANSCEND
THE EVIL.

402
00:23:44,506 --> 00:23:45,507
IT SHALL BE DONE.

403
00:23:45,632 --> 00:23:49,220
SO IT HAS BEEN
SINCE THE BEGINNING.

404
00:23:49,345 --> 00:23:50,679
HE DOESN'T HEAR YOU,
CAPTAIN.

405
00:23:50,804 --> 00:23:52,973
MAYBE HE'LL HEAR THIS.

406
00:23:53,099 --> 00:23:55,017
PUT THAT AWAY.

407
00:23:56,269 --> 00:23:59,105
LANDRU...
LISTEN TO ME.

408
00:23:59,230 --> 00:24:03,901
YOU WILL BE ABSORBED.

409
00:24:04,026 --> 00:24:06,737
YOUR INDIVIDUALITY
WILL MERGE

410
00:24:06,862 --> 00:24:09,740
INTO THE UNITY OF GOOD,

411
00:24:09,865 --> 00:24:11,533
AND IN YOUR SUBMERGENCE

412
00:24:11,658 --> 00:24:14,161
INTO THE COMMON BEING
OF THE BODY,

413
00:24:14,287 --> 00:24:16,538
YOU WILL FIND CONTENTMENT

414
00:24:16,663 --> 00:24:19,166
AND FULFILLMENT.

415
00:24:19,292 --> 00:24:21,543
YOU WILL EXPERIENCE...

416
00:24:21,668 --> 00:24:24,462
THE ABSOLUTE GOOD.

417
00:24:24,588 --> 00:24:27,591
OHH...

418
00:24:27,716 --> 00:24:29,635
[HIGH-PITCHED WHIRRING]

419
00:24:55,995 --> 00:24:57,955
CAPTAIN'S LOG.

420
00:24:58,080 --> 00:24:59,999
STARDATE 3157.4--

421
00:25:00,124 --> 00:25:01,959
THE ENTERPRISE,

422
00:25:02,084 --> 00:25:03,169
STILL UNDER ATTACK
BY SOME SORT OF HEAT RAYS

423
00:25:03,294 --> 00:25:05,545
FROM THE SURFACE
OF BETA 3,

424
00:25:05,671 --> 00:25:09,133
IS NOW BEING COMMANDED BY
ENGINEERING OFFICER SCOTT.

425
00:25:09,258 --> 00:25:11,427
THE SHORE PARTY
HAS BEEN TAKEN

426
00:25:11,551 --> 00:25:14,596
BY THE CREATURE
CALLED LANDRU.

427
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:02,644
MR. SPOCK.

428
00:26:06,690 --> 00:26:08,566
WAKE UP.

429
00:26:09,109 --> 00:26:11,153
MR. LESLIE.

430
00:26:15,408 --> 00:26:17,326
WHERE'S DR. McCOY?

431
00:26:17,451 --> 00:26:18,702
HE WAS GONE
WHEN I WOKE UP,

432
00:26:18,827 --> 00:26:19,995
ALONG WITH
THE OTHER GUARD

433
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:23,040
AND MR. O'NEIL.

434
00:26:23,165 --> 00:26:25,583
I SHOULD SAY
THEY'VE BEEN HERE
AND BEEN REMOVED.

435
00:26:29,671 --> 00:26:32,091
BUT WHERE IS "HERE"?

436
00:26:32,216 --> 00:26:35,010
EVIDENTLY
A MAXIMUM-SECURITY
ESTABLISHMENT.

437
00:26:36,678 --> 00:26:37,930
ARE YOU ARMED?

438
00:26:38,055 --> 00:26:38,847
ALL OUR PHASERS
ARE GONE.

439
00:26:38,972 --> 00:26:41,016
I CHECKED.

440
00:26:42,184 --> 00:26:43,561
THAT'S LOCKED.

441
00:26:43,685 --> 00:26:45,354
OHH.

442
00:26:49,024 --> 00:26:50,901
OH, DOES
MY HEAD ACHE.

443
00:26:51,026 --> 00:26:53,237
THE NATURAL RESULT
OF BEING SUBJECTED
TO A HYPERSONIC.

444
00:26:53,362 --> 00:26:55,155
OH. IS THAT
WHAT IT WAS?

445
00:26:55,281 --> 00:26:56,532
SOUND WAVES.

446
00:26:56,656 --> 00:26:57,657
STRONGER, THEY
MIGHT HAVE KILLED.

447
00:26:57,783 --> 00:26:59,868
AS IT WAS, THEY MERELY
RENDERED US UNCONSCIOUS.

448
00:26:59,993 --> 00:27:01,870
ENOUGH ANALYSIS.

449
00:27:01,995 --> 00:27:04,582
LET'S THINK OF A WAY
TO GET OUT OF HERE.

450
00:27:06,584 --> 00:27:08,335
WHAT ABOUT
THE LAWGIVERS' INABILITY

451
00:27:08,461 --> 00:27:10,588
TO COPE WITH
THE UNEXPECTED?

452
00:27:11,964 --> 00:27:14,383
YOU SHOULDN'T DEPEND
ON THAT HAPPENING
AGAIN, CAPTAIN.

453
00:27:14,508 --> 00:27:16,343
IN A SOCIETY
AS WELL ORGANIZED

454
00:27:16,469 --> 00:27:18,137
AS THIS ONE
SEEMS TO BE,

455
00:27:18,262 --> 00:27:22,057
I CANNOT CONCEIVE
OF SUCH AN OVERSIGHT
GOING UNCORRECTED.

456
00:27:24,518 --> 00:27:26,937
INTERESTING, HOWEVER--

457
00:27:27,062 --> 00:27:29,148
THEIR REACTION
TO YOUR DEFIANCE

458
00:27:29,273 --> 00:27:30,732
WAS REMARKABLY SIMILAR

459
00:27:30,857 --> 00:27:32,318
TO THE REACTION
OF A COMPUTER

460
00:27:32,443 --> 00:27:36,113
WHEN FED INSUFFICIENT
OR CONTRADICTORY DATA.

461
00:27:36,238 --> 00:27:38,282
ARE YOU SUGGESTING
THAT THE LAWGIVERS
ARE MERE COMPUTERS,

462
00:27:38,407 --> 00:27:42,328
THAT...
THEY AREN'T HUMAN?

463
00:27:42,453 --> 00:27:44,037
QUITE HUMAN,
CAPTAIN.

464
00:27:44,163 --> 00:27:46,039
IT'S SIMPLY
THAT ALL THE FACTS
ARE NOT YET IN.

465
00:27:46,165 --> 00:27:48,542
THERE ARE GAPS.

466
00:27:48,666 --> 00:27:51,003
[DOOR OPENS]

467
00:28:04,975 --> 00:28:07,561
DOC. HOW--

468
00:28:07,685 --> 00:28:09,146
HELLO, FRIEND.

469
00:28:09,271 --> 00:28:11,982
WE WERE TOLD
TO WAIT HERE.

470
00:28:13,275 --> 00:28:14,776
DOC.

471
00:28:16,069 --> 00:28:19,615
CAN I HELP YOU,
FRIEND?

472
00:28:20,157 --> 00:28:21,783
DON'T YOU KNOW ME?

473
00:28:21,908 --> 00:28:24,328
WE ALL KNOW
ONE ANOTHER

474
00:28:24,453 --> 00:28:26,038
IN LANDRU.

475
00:28:26,163 --> 00:28:28,582
LIKE SULU.

476
00:28:32,836 --> 00:28:34,963
THINK, MAN.

477
00:28:35,088 --> 00:28:36,173
THE ENTERPRISE.

478
00:28:36,298 --> 00:28:37,757
THE SHIP.

479
00:28:37,883 --> 00:28:39,759
REMEMBER?

480
00:28:39,885 --> 00:28:42,971
YOU SPEAK VERY
STRANGELY, FRIEND.

481
00:28:43,096 --> 00:28:43,972
ARE YOU FROM AWAY?

482
00:28:44,097 --> 00:28:46,308
YOU DO REMEMBER!

483
00:28:49,603 --> 00:28:52,523
ASK LANDRU.

484
00:28:52,648 --> 00:28:54,692
HE REMEMBERS.

485
00:28:54,816 --> 00:28:57,194
HE KNOWS,
AND HE WATCHES.

486
00:29:02,074 --> 00:29:04,243
YOU ARE STRANGE.

487
00:29:04,368 --> 00:29:06,579
ARE YOU NOT
OF THE BODY?

488
00:29:26,098 --> 00:29:26,765
COME.

489
00:29:26,890 --> 00:29:28,559
NO.

490
00:29:28,684 --> 00:29:30,603
THEN YOU WILL DIE.

491
00:29:33,397 --> 00:29:35,857
IT'S BEEN
CORRECTED, CAPTAIN.

492
00:29:35,982 --> 00:29:38,318
YOU'D BETTER GO.

493
00:29:38,444 --> 00:29:41,154
ALL RIGHT.

494
00:29:41,280 --> 00:29:42,822
WORK ON BONES.

495
00:29:42,948 --> 00:29:43,865
SEE IF YOU CAN'T--

496
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:45,867
COME.

497
00:30:03,552 --> 00:30:07,806
DR. McCOY,
WHAT WILL HAPPEN TO HIM?

498
00:30:09,683 --> 00:30:11,810
HE GOES TO JOY,

499
00:30:11,935 --> 00:30:13,562
PEACE,

500
00:30:13,687 --> 00:30:15,147
AND TRANQUILITY.

501
00:30:15,272 --> 00:30:16,273
HE GOES
TO MEET LANDRU.

502
00:30:16,398 --> 00:30:19,943
HAPPINESS
IS TO ALL OF US

503
00:30:20,068 --> 00:30:22,571
BLESSED BY LANDRU.

504
00:30:31,079 --> 00:30:32,956
I AM MARPLON.

505
00:30:33,081 --> 00:30:34,750
IT IS YOUR HOUR.

506
00:30:34,874 --> 00:30:36,543
HAPPY COMMUNING.

507
00:30:36,669 --> 00:30:39,171
WITH THANKS.

508
00:30:39,296 --> 00:30:42,007
HAPPY COMMUNING.

509
00:30:54,311 --> 00:30:56,355
WELL?

510
00:31:02,068 --> 00:31:04,196
IMPOSSIBLE.

511
00:31:04,321 --> 00:31:06,990
HE'S UNDER EXTREMELY
POWERFUL CONTROL.

512
00:31:09,034 --> 00:31:11,578
ARE WE JUST
GOING TO STAND HERE?

513
00:31:12,830 --> 00:31:15,541
LITTLE ELSE
WE CAN DO...

514
00:31:15,666 --> 00:31:17,334
UNLESS YOU CAN
THINK OF A WAY

515
00:31:17,459 --> 00:31:19,378
TO GET THROUGH
THAT DOOR.

516
00:31:21,254 --> 00:31:22,756
WELL, THIS IS
SIMPLY RIDICULOUS--

517
00:31:22,881 --> 00:31:24,132
A BUNCH OF
STONE-AGE CHARACTERS

518
00:31:24,257 --> 00:31:25,759
RUNNING AROUND
IN ROBES.

519
00:31:25,884 --> 00:31:27,135
AND APPARENTLY
COMMANDING POWERS

520
00:31:27,260 --> 00:31:28,887
FAR BEYOND
OUR COMPREHENSION.

521
00:31:29,012 --> 00:31:31,181
NOT SIMPLE.

522
00:31:31,306 --> 00:31:32,974
NOT RIDICULOUS.

523
00:31:33,099 --> 00:31:35,394
VERY, VERY DANGEROUS.

524
00:31:45,278 --> 00:31:47,531
YOU...

525
00:31:47,656 --> 00:31:49,991
COME.

526
00:32:21,273 --> 00:32:22,566
JOY TO YOU, FRIEND.

527
00:32:22,691 --> 00:32:27,112
PEACE AND CONTENTMENT
WILL FILL YOU.

528
00:32:27,237 --> 00:32:30,574
YOU WILL KNOW
THE PEACE OF LANDRU.

529
00:32:58,101 --> 00:33:01,438
HAVE NO FEAR, FRIEND.
THE EFFECT IS HARMLESS.

530
00:33:01,563 --> 00:33:02,981
MY NAME IS MARPLON.

531
00:33:03,106 --> 00:33:04,775
I WAS TOO LATE TO SAVE
YOUR FIRST TWO FRIENDS.

532
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:06,359
THEY HAVE BEEN ABSORBED.

533
00:33:06,485 --> 00:33:08,654
BEWARE OF THEM.

534
00:33:17,913 --> 00:33:19,372
WHAT ABOUT THE CAPTAIN?

535
00:33:19,498 --> 00:33:21,708
HE IS UNHARMED,
UNCHANGED.

536
00:33:21,834 --> 00:33:25,170
I AM THE THIRD MAN
IN REGER'S TRIAD.

537
00:33:25,295 --> 00:33:27,714
WE HAVE BEEN AWAITING
YOUR RETURN.

538
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:29,382
WE ARE NOT ARCHONS,
MARPLON.

539
00:33:29,508 --> 00:33:31,176
WHATEVER YOU MAY
CALL YOURSELVES,

540
00:33:31,301 --> 00:33:33,804
YOU ARE IN FULFILLMENT
OF PROPHECY.

541
00:33:33,929 --> 00:33:35,054
WE ASK YOUR HELP.

542
00:33:35,180 --> 00:33:36,515
WHERE IS REGER?

543
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:38,391
HE WILL JOIN US.

544
00:33:38,517 --> 00:33:41,019
HE IS IMMUNE
TO ABSORPTION.

545
00:33:41,144 --> 00:33:42,562
HURRY.

546
00:33:42,688 --> 00:33:43,897
WE HAVE NOT
MUCH TIME.

547
00:33:44,022 --> 00:33:45,524
WHO IS LANDRU?

548
00:33:45,649 --> 00:33:48,777
I CANNOT ANSWER
YOUR QUESTIONS NOW.

549
00:33:48,902 --> 00:33:51,404
LANDRU, HE WILL HEAR.

550
00:33:52,698 --> 00:33:55,200
HERE ARE YOUR WEAPONS.

551
00:33:55,325 --> 00:33:57,744
YOU MAY NEED THEM.

552
00:33:59,621 --> 00:34:04,209
BEHAVE AS YOU SAW
YOUR CAPTAIN BEHAVE.

553
00:34:04,334 --> 00:34:06,628
IT IS DONE.

554
00:34:08,171 --> 00:34:10,089
JOY BE WITH YOU.

555
00:34:10,215 --> 00:34:13,635
PEACE AND
CONTENTMENT.

556
00:34:31,319 --> 00:34:32,153
CAPTAIN--

557
00:34:32,278 --> 00:34:35,908
PEACE AND TRANQUILITY
TO YOU.

558
00:34:37,116 --> 00:34:38,994
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

559
00:34:39,118 --> 00:34:40,579
QUITE ALL RIGHT.

560
00:34:40,704 --> 00:34:41,997
BE CAREFUL
OF DR. McCOY.

561
00:34:42,121 --> 00:34:43,832
I UNDERSTAND.

562
00:34:44,917 --> 00:34:45,959
LANDRU.

563
00:34:46,084 --> 00:34:48,378
I AM FORMULATING
A THEORY, CAPTAIN.

564
00:34:48,503 --> 00:34:49,546
AND?

565
00:34:51,089 --> 00:34:52,632
NOT HERE.
THE DOCTOR.

566
00:34:54,509 --> 00:34:58,722
YOU SPEAK IN
STRANGE WHISPERS.

567
00:34:58,847 --> 00:35:02,017
THIS IS NOT THE WAY
OF LANDRU.

568
00:35:02,141 --> 00:35:04,770
JOY BE YOURS,

569
00:35:04,895 --> 00:35:07,188
AND TRANQUILITY,
MY FRIEND.

570
00:35:07,313 --> 00:35:09,733
AND PEACE
AND HARMONY.

571
00:35:09,858 --> 00:35:11,777
ARE YOU
OF THE BODY?

572
00:35:11,902 --> 00:35:14,195
THE BODY IS ONE.

573
00:35:15,488 --> 00:35:17,574
BLESSED
BE THE BODY

574
00:35:17,699 --> 00:35:20,577
AND HEALTH TO ALL
OF ITS PARTS.

575
00:35:20,702 --> 00:35:22,537
MY FRIENDS...

576
00:35:27,709 --> 00:35:29,586
WHAT IS YOUR THEORY,
MR. SPOCK?

577
00:35:29,711 --> 00:35:31,838
THIS IS A SOULLESS
SOCIETY, CAPTAIN.

578
00:35:31,964 --> 00:35:33,966
IT HAS NO SPIRIT,
NO SPARK.

579
00:35:34,091 --> 00:35:36,009
ALL IS INDEED PEACE
AND TRANQUILITY--

580
00:35:36,134 --> 00:35:39,471
THE PEACE OF THE FACTORY,
THE TRANQUILITY
OF THE MACHINE,

581
00:35:39,596 --> 00:35:41,556
ALL PARTS
WORKING IN UNISON.

582
00:35:41,681 --> 00:35:44,643
AND WHEN SOMETHING
UNEXPLAINED HAPPENS...

583
00:35:48,521 --> 00:35:50,398
THEIR ROUTINE
IS DISRUPTED?

584
00:35:50,523 --> 00:35:51,984
UNTIL NEW ORDERS
ARE RECEIVED.

585
00:35:52,109 --> 00:35:53,359
THE QUESTION IS,

586
00:35:53,485 --> 00:35:54,527
WHO GIVES
THOSE ORDERS?

587
00:35:54,653 --> 00:35:56,071
LANDRU.

588
00:35:56,195 --> 00:35:58,156
THERE IS NO LANDRU,
CAPTAIN,

589
00:35:58,281 --> 00:35:59,491
NOT IN
THE HUMAN SENSE.

590
00:35:59,616 --> 00:36:03,829
YOU'RE THINKING
THE SAME THING I AM.

591
00:36:05,122 --> 00:36:06,247
MR. SPOCK,

592
00:36:06,372 --> 00:36:08,959
THE PLUG MUST BE PULLED.

593
00:36:09,084 --> 00:36:10,585
SIR?

594
00:36:10,710 --> 00:36:12,420
LANDRU MUST DIE.

595
00:36:12,545 --> 00:36:16,091
CAPTAIN,
OUR PRIME DIRECTIVE
OF NONINTERFERENCE.

596
00:36:16,215 --> 00:36:19,636
THAT REFERS TO
A LIVING, GROWING CULTURE.

597
00:36:19,761 --> 00:36:22,055
DO YOU THINK THIS ONE IS?

598
00:36:31,481 --> 00:36:33,566
JOY TO YOU ALL,
FRIENDS.

599
00:36:33,692 --> 00:36:36,402
IT IS THE GIFT
OF LANDRU.

600
00:36:46,705 --> 00:36:48,206
I BROUGHT YOUR
SIGNALING DEVICES.

601
00:36:48,331 --> 00:36:49,791
YOU MAY NEED THEM.

602
00:36:49,916 --> 00:36:52,627
WHAT WE REALLY NEED
IS MORE INFORMATION
ABOUT LANDRU.

603
00:36:55,296 --> 00:36:58,008
YOU SAID YOU WANTED US
TO HELP YOU.

604
00:36:58,133 --> 00:36:59,384
PROPHECY SAYS--

605
00:36:59,509 --> 00:37:01,761
NEVER MIND WHAT
THE PROPHECY SAYS.

606
00:37:01,887 --> 00:37:03,847
IF YOU WANT
TO BE LIBERATED
FROM LANDRU,

607
00:37:03,972 --> 00:37:06,224
WE'LL NEED
YOUR HELP.

608
00:37:06,349 --> 00:37:07,767
CAPTAIN.

609
00:37:09,477 --> 00:37:10,228
YOU'RE NOT OF THE BODY!

610
00:37:10,353 --> 00:37:12,230
PEACE...
YOU'RE NOT!

611
00:37:12,355 --> 00:37:13,565
TO YOU, FRIEND.

612
00:37:13,690 --> 00:37:14,774
LAWGIVERS!

613
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:15,984
PEACE.

614
00:37:16,109 --> 00:37:17,152
LAWGIVERS!

615
00:37:17,276 --> 00:37:19,278
TRAITOR! TRAITORS!

616
00:37:19,404 --> 00:37:21,573
TRAITORS!

617
00:37:21,698 --> 00:37:23,116
DOC, I DON'T WANT
TO HURT YOU.

618
00:37:23,241 --> 00:37:24,617
TRAITORS!

619
00:37:27,370 --> 00:37:28,788
AW, DOC...

620
00:37:30,331 --> 00:37:32,250
SPOCK.

621
00:37:44,721 --> 00:37:46,472
ISN'T THAT
SOMEWHAT OLD-FASHIONED?

622
00:37:46,598 --> 00:37:48,808
THE ROBES.

623
00:37:51,895 --> 00:37:54,773
WHERE IS LANDRU?

624
00:37:54,898 --> 00:37:55,982
NO. NO.

625
00:37:56,108 --> 00:37:57,525
WHERE DO WE FIND HIM?

626
00:37:59,819 --> 00:38:02,989
WE DO NOT SEE HIM.

627
00:38:04,323 --> 00:38:07,160
WE HEAR HIM

628
00:38:07,285 --> 00:38:09,955
IN THE HALL
OF AUDIENCES.

629
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,664
IN THIS BUILDING?

630
00:38:15,501 --> 00:38:16,586
YES.

631
00:38:16,711 --> 00:38:18,713
YOU'RE GOING TO
TAKE US THERE.

632
00:38:18,838 --> 00:38:20,257
OH.

633
00:38:20,381 --> 00:38:22,801
SPOCK, CALL THE ENTERPRISE.

634
00:38:22,926 --> 00:38:24,970
OH!

635
00:38:25,095 --> 00:38:28,014
SNAP OUT OF IT!

636
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:29,808
START ACTING LIKE MEN.

637
00:38:29,933 --> 00:38:31,893
SPOCK TO ENTERPRISE.
STATUS REPORT.

638
00:38:32,018 --> 00:38:35,021
MR. SPOCK, I'VE BEEN
TRYING TO REACH YOU.

639
00:38:35,147 --> 00:38:36,273
REPORT, SCOTT.

640
00:38:36,397 --> 00:38:38,775
THE ORBIT'S
STILL DECAYING.

641
00:38:38,900 --> 00:38:40,359
GIVE IT SIX HOURS,
MORE OR LESS.

642
00:38:40,485 --> 00:38:42,070
THOSE HEAT BEAMS
ARE STILL ON US.

643
00:38:42,195 --> 00:38:43,696
YOU'VE GOT TO CUT
THEM OFF, MR. SPOCK,

644
00:38:43,822 --> 00:38:45,073
OR WE'LL COOK,
ONE WAY OR ANOTHER.

645
00:38:45,198 --> 00:38:47,075
SCOTTY,
STAND BY.

646
00:38:47,200 --> 00:38:49,119
WE'RE DOING
THE BEST WE CAN.

647
00:38:49,244 --> 00:38:50,578
HOW'S MR. SULU?

648
00:38:50,703 --> 00:38:53,581
HE'S PEACEFUL ENOUGH,
BUT HE WORRIES ME.

649
00:38:53,706 --> 00:38:55,416
PUT A GUARD ON HIM.

650
00:38:55,541 --> 00:38:56,960
ON SULU?

651
00:38:57,085 --> 00:38:58,837
THAT'S AN ORDER.

652
00:38:58,962 --> 00:39:00,588
WATCH HIM.

653
00:39:00,713 --> 00:39:01,840
CAPTAIN OUT.

654
00:39:01,965 --> 00:39:03,842
CAPTAIN.

655
00:39:06,344 --> 00:39:08,013
ALL RIGHT.

656
00:39:08,138 --> 00:39:10,015
ABOUT LANDRU.

657
00:39:10,140 --> 00:39:13,601
WELL...THERE WAS WAR,

658
00:39:13,726 --> 00:39:14,435
CONVULSIONS.

659
00:39:14,560 --> 00:39:17,230
THE WORLD WAS
DESTROYING ITSELF.

660
00:39:17,355 --> 00:39:19,191
LANDRU WAS OUR LEADER.

661
00:39:19,316 --> 00:39:21,400
HE SAW THE TRUTH.

662
00:39:21,526 --> 00:39:23,444
HE CHANGED THE WORLD.

663
00:39:23,569 --> 00:39:25,113
HE TOOK US BACK,

664
00:39:25,238 --> 00:39:27,365
BACK TO A SIMPLE TIME,

665
00:39:27,490 --> 00:39:28,992
A TIME OF PEACE
AND TRANQUILITY.

666
00:39:29,117 --> 00:39:31,077
WHAT HAPPENED
TO HIM?

667
00:39:32,162 --> 00:39:34,080
HE'S STILL ALIVE.

668
00:39:34,206 --> 00:39:37,209
HE IS HERE NOW.

669
00:39:37,334 --> 00:39:39,627
HE SEES. HE HEARS.

670
00:39:41,713 --> 00:39:45,217
WE HAVE DESTROYED
OURSELVES.

671
00:39:45,342 --> 00:39:46,384
PLEASE...

672
00:39:46,509 --> 00:39:48,345
NO MORE.

673
00:39:49,512 --> 00:39:52,098
YOU SAID
YOU WANTED FREEDOM.

674
00:39:52,224 --> 00:39:54,142
IT'S TIME YOU LEARNED THAT
FREEDOM IS NEVER A GIFT.

675
00:39:54,267 --> 00:39:55,852
IT HAS TO BE EARNED.

676
00:39:55,977 --> 00:39:57,520
COME ON.

677
00:39:57,645 --> 00:39:59,147
WE'RE GOING TO
FIND LANDRU.

678
00:39:59,272 --> 00:40:01,191
NO! NO!
I WAS WRONG!

679
00:40:01,316 --> 00:40:02,775
I SUBMIT!

680
00:40:02,901 --> 00:40:04,194
I BEAR MYSELF
TO THE WILL OF LANDRU!

681
00:40:04,319 --> 00:40:06,029
IT'S TOO LATE FOR THAT.

682
00:40:06,154 --> 00:40:06,905
NO! NO! GIVE US HELP!

683
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:10,200
HELP ME!

684
00:40:10,325 --> 00:40:11,492
ALL RIGHT,

685
00:40:11,617 --> 00:40:12,994
IT'S UP TO YOU.

686
00:40:13,119 --> 00:40:14,787
TAKE US TO LANDRU.

687
00:40:28,093 --> 00:40:30,887
THIS IS THE HALL
OF AUDIENCES.

688
00:40:31,012 --> 00:40:32,722
OPEN IT.

689
00:40:32,847 --> 00:40:34,891
BUT THIS IS LANDRU.

690
00:40:35,016 --> 00:40:36,893
OPEN IT.

691
00:40:58,831 --> 00:41:01,834
LANDRU SPEAKS HERE.

692
00:41:08,507 --> 00:41:10,427
LANDRU!

693
00:41:12,720 --> 00:41:14,431
LANDRU!

694
00:41:14,555 --> 00:41:16,849
WE ARE THE ARCHONS!

695
00:41:18,017 --> 00:41:20,395
WE ARE THE ARCHONS!
WE'VE COME TO SPEAK!

696
00:41:20,519 --> 00:41:21,687
WE ARE
THE ARCHONS.

697
00:41:21,813 --> 00:41:23,856
WE WANT TO
TALK TO YOU.

698
00:41:23,982 --> 00:41:25,566
LANDRU!

699
00:41:25,691 --> 00:41:27,152
HE COMES!

700
00:41:41,458 --> 00:41:43,751
DESPITE MY EFFORTS
TO SAVE YOU,

701
00:41:43,876 --> 00:41:45,586
YOU HAVE INVADED
THE BODY,

702
00:41:45,711 --> 00:41:47,255
AND YOU ARE
CAUSING GREAT HARM.

703
00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:49,466
WE HAVE NO INTENTION
OF CAUSING HARM.

704
00:41:49,590 --> 00:41:53,219
OBLITERATION
IS NECESSARY.

705
00:41:53,345 --> 00:41:56,764
THE INFECTION IS STRONG.

706
00:41:56,889 --> 00:42:00,352
FOR THE GOOD
OF THE BODY,

707
00:42:00,477 --> 00:42:02,854
YOU MUST DIE.

708
00:42:03,980 --> 00:42:06,024
IT IS...

709
00:42:06,149 --> 00:42:08,026
A GREAT SORROW.

710
00:42:08,151 --> 00:42:09,486
WE DO NOT INTEND TO DIE.

711
00:42:09,610 --> 00:42:12,155
ALL WHO SAW YOU,

712
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:15,033
ALL WHO KNOW
OF YOUR PRESENCE HERE

713
00:42:15,158 --> 00:42:18,370
MUST BE EXCISED.

714
00:42:18,495 --> 00:42:22,081
THE MEMORY OF THE BODY
WILL BE CLEANSED.

715
00:42:23,916 --> 00:42:25,210
LISTEN TO ME.

716
00:42:25,335 --> 00:42:26,794
USELESS, CAPTAIN.

717
00:42:26,919 --> 00:42:28,838
A PROJECTION.

718
00:42:30,089 --> 00:42:32,509
YES, MR. SPOCK.

719
00:42:32,633 --> 00:42:37,430
LET'S HAVE A LOOK
AT THE PROJECTOR.

720
00:42:56,574 --> 00:42:58,951
OF COURSE.

721
00:42:59,077 --> 00:43:01,787
IT HAD TO BE.

722
00:43:06,959 --> 00:43:08,878
LANDRU.

723
00:43:09,003 --> 00:43:10,922
A MACHINE.

724
00:43:11,047 --> 00:43:14,592
THIS WHOLE SOCIETY
IS A MACHINE'S CONCEPT
OF PERFECTION--

725
00:43:14,717 --> 00:43:16,219
PEACE, HARMONY...

726
00:43:16,344 --> 00:43:18,388
BUT NO SOUL.

727
00:43:18,513 --> 00:43:21,307
I AM LANDRU.
YOU HAVE INTRUDED.

728
00:43:21,433 --> 00:43:25,603
PULL OUT ITS PLUG,
MR. SPOCK.

729
00:43:31,276 --> 00:43:33,570
YOUR DEVICES
HAVE BEEN NEUTRALIZED.

730
00:43:33,694 --> 00:43:35,988
SO IT SHALL BE WITH YOU.

731
00:43:36,114 --> 00:43:38,950
I AM LANDRU.

732
00:43:39,075 --> 00:43:42,787
LANDRU DIED
6,000 YEARS AGO.

733
00:43:42,912 --> 00:43:44,205
I AM LANDRU.

734
00:43:44,330 --> 00:43:45,248
I AM HE.

735
00:43:45,373 --> 00:43:47,584
ALL THAT HE WAS
I AM--

736
00:43:47,708 --> 00:43:49,377
HIS EXPERIENCE,
HIS KNOWLEDGE.

737
00:43:49,502 --> 00:43:51,337
BUT NOT
HIS WISDOM.

738
00:43:51,463 --> 00:43:53,548
HE MAY HAVE
PROGRAMMED YOU,

739
00:43:53,672 --> 00:43:56,759
BUT HE COULD NOT
HAVE GIVEN YOU
A SOUL.

740
00:43:56,884 --> 00:43:58,344
YOU ARE
A MACHINE.

741
00:43:58,470 --> 00:44:01,889
YOUR STATEMENT
IS IRRELEVANT.

742
00:44:02,014 --> 00:44:03,808
YOU WILL...

743
00:44:03,933 --> 00:44:04,976
BE...

744
00:44:05,101 --> 00:44:06,603
OBLITERATED.

745
00:44:06,727 --> 00:44:09,939
THE GOOD OF THE BODY
IS THE PRIME DIRECTIVE.

746
00:44:10,064 --> 00:44:12,984
THE GOOD OF THE BODY, CAPTAIN.
THAT'S THE KEY.

747
00:44:16,321 --> 00:44:17,530
YES.

748
00:44:24,537 --> 00:44:25,913
WHAT IS THE GOOD?

749
00:44:26,038 --> 00:44:28,791
I AM LANDRU.

750
00:44:28,916 --> 00:44:30,543
LANDRU IS DEAD.
YOU ARE A MACHINE.

751
00:44:30,668 --> 00:44:33,379
A QUESTION HAS
BEEN PUT TO YOU.
ANSWER IT.

