00:45:14,879 --> 00:45:17,298
INSUFFICIENT DATA.

769
00:45:17,423 --> 00:45:19,758
WITHOUT
FREEDOM OF CHOICE,

770
00:45:19,884 --> 00:45:21,093
THERE IS
NO CREATIVITY.

