00:45:42,073 --> 00:45:43,575
NOT NECESSARY,
CAPTAIN.

783
00:45:43,700 --> 00:45:44,950
THEY HAVE
NO GUIDANCE,

784
00:45:45,076 --> 00:45:47,203
POSSIBLY FOR
