00:45:53,209 --> 00:45:55,044
ANSWER THE QUESTION.

787
00:45:55,169 --> 00:45:58,005
PEACE, ORDER,
AND TRANQUILITY

788
00:45:58,130 --> 00:45:59,840
ARE MAINTAINED.

789
00:45:59,965 --> 00:46:01,800
THE BODY LIVES,

790
00:46:01,926 --> 00:46:05,263
BUT I RESERVE
CREATIVITY TO ME.

