00:46:05,388 --> 00:46:06,847
THEN THE BODY DIES.

792
00:46:06,972 --> 00:46:09,850
CREATIVITY IS NECESSARY
FOR THE HEALTH OF THE BODY.

793
00:46:09,975 --> 00:46:11,227
THIS...

794
00:46:11,352 --> 00:46:11,936
IS...

795
00:46:12,061 --> 00:46:13,730
IMPOSSIBLE!

796
00:46:13,854 --> 00:46:15,856
IS THIS
TRULY LANDRU?

797
00:46:15,981 --> 00:46:17,567
WHAT'S LEFT OF HIM

798
00:46:17,692 --> 00:46:19,151
AFTER HE BUILT
AND PROGRAMMED

799
00:46:19,277 --> 00:46:21,487
THIS MACHINE
6,000 YEARS AGO.

800
00:46:22,363 --> 00:46:24,574
YOU MUST CREATE
THE GOOD.

801
00:46:24,699 --> 00:46:25,991
THAT IS THE WILL
OF LANDRU,

802
00:46:26,117 --> 00:46:27,410
NOTHING ELSE.

803
00:46:27,535 --> 00:46:28,411
BUT THERE IS EVIL.

804
00:46:28,536 --> 00:46:30,955
THEN THE EVIL
MUST BE DESTROYED.

805
00:46:31,080 --> 00:46:33,374
THAT IS
THE PRIME DIRECTIVE,

806
00:46:33,499 --> 00:46:36,419
AND YOU
ARE THE EVIL.

807
00:46:38,087 --> 00:46:38,879
I THINK.

808
00:46:39,004 --> 00:46:40,506
I LIVE.

809
00:46:40,632 --> 00:46:42,550
YOU ARE THE EVIL.

810
00:46:42,675 --> 00:46:44,385
THE EVIL
MUST BE DESTROYED.

811
00:46:44,510 --> 00:46:46,345
FULFILL
THE PRIME DIRECTIVE.

812
00:46:46,471 --> 00:46:47,513
YOU...
LANDRU, HELP ME!

813
00:46:47,639 --> 00:46:49,181
ARE THE EVIL.

814
00:46:49,307 --> 00:46:51,392
FULFILL
THE PRIME DIRECTIVE.

815
00:46:51,517 --> 00:46:53,603
HELP ME! HELP ME!
