816
00:47:19,836 --> 00:47:21,880
WELL, MARPLON,
YOU'RE ON YOUR OWN NOW.

817
00:47:22,006 --> 00:47:23,424
I HOPE
YOU'RE UP TO IT.

818
00:47:23,549 --> 00:47:25,050
YOU CAN GET RID
OF THOSE ROBES.

819
00:47:25,176 --> 00:47:26,385
AND IF I WERE YOU,

820
00:47:26,511 --> 00:47:29,555
I'D START LOOKING
FOR ANOTHER JOB.

821
00:47:29,681 --> 00:47:31,641
KIRK TO ENTERPRISE.
COME IN.

822
00:47:31,766 --> 00:47:33,810
CAPTAIN,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

823
00:47:33,934 --> 00:47:34,435
WHAT ABOUT THE SHIP?

824
00:47:34,560 --> 00:47:36,688
THE HEAT RAYS HAVE GONE,
CAPTAIN,

825
00:47:36,813 --> 00:47:39,982
AND MR. SULU'S
BACK TO NORMAL.

826
00:47:40,107 --> 00:47:41,651
RELIEVING YOU.

827
00:47:41,776 --> 00:47:43,444
EXCELLENT, SCOTTY.

828
00:47:43,569 --> 00:47:45,904
STAND BY TO BEAM UP
LANDING PARTY.

829
00:47:46,030 --> 00:47:47,573
LET'S GO SEE HOW THE
OTHERS ARE DOING.

830
00:47:47,699 --> 00:47:49,826
MARPLON
CAN FINISH UP HERE.

831
00:47:51,703 --> 00:47:52,995
CAPTAIN'S LOG.

832
00:47:53,120 --> 00:47:55,665
STARDATE 3158.7--

833
00:47:55,790 --> 00:47:59,335
THE ENTERPRISE IS
PREPARING TO LEAVE BETA 3

834
00:47:59,460 --> 00:48:01,086
IN STARSYSTEM C-111.

835
00:48:01,212 --> 00:48:03,130
SOCIOLOGIST LINDSTROM

836
00:48:03,255 --> 00:48:06,258
IS REMAINING BEHIND
WITH A PARTY OF EXPERTS

837
00:48:06,384 --> 00:48:08,803
WHO WILL HELP RESTORE
THE PLANET'S CULTURE

838
00:48:08,927 --> 00:48:10,388
TO A HUMAN FORM.

839
00:48:10,513 --> 00:48:11,597
MARVELOUS.

840
00:48:11,723 --> 00:48:12,765
WHAT?

841
00:48:12,889 --> 00:48:14,809
THE LATE LANDRU,
CAPTAIN,

842
00:48:14,933 --> 00:48:16,811
A MARVELOUS FEAT
OF ENGINEERING--

843
00:48:16,935 --> 00:48:18,270
A COMPUTER CAPABLE
OF DIRECTING THE LIVES

844
00:48:18,396 --> 00:48:20,147
OF MILLIONS
OF HUMAN BEINGS.

845
00:48:20,272 --> 00:48:21,982
BUT ONLY A MACHINE,
MR. SPOCK.

846
00:48:22,107 --> 00:48:23,401
THE ORIGINAL LANDRU
PROGRAMMED IT WITH
ALL HIS KNOWLEDGE,

847
00:48:23,526 --> 00:48:25,778
BUT HE COULDN'T
GIVE IT HIS WISDOM,

848
00:48:25,902 --> 00:48:27,572
HIS COMPASSION,
HIS UNDERSTANDING,

849
00:48:27,697 --> 00:48:29,948
HIS SOUL, MR. SPOCK.

850
00:48:30,074 --> 00:48:32,410
PREDICTABLY
METAPHYSICAL.

851
00:48:32,535 --> 00:48:33,411
I PREFER THE CONCRETE,

852
00:48:33,536 --> 00:48:35,747
THE GRASPABLE,
THE PROVABLE.

853
00:48:35,872 --> 00:48:38,957
YOU WOULD MAKE
A SPLENDID COMPUTER,
MR. SPOCK.

854
00:48:39,083 --> 00:48:40,626
THAT IS VERY KIND
OF YOU, CAPTAIN.

855
00:48:40,752 --> 00:48:42,378
CAPTAIN...

856
00:48:42,503 --> 00:48:44,422
MR. LINDSTROM
FROM THE SURFACE.

857
00:48:44,547 --> 00:48:45,798
YES, LINDSTROM.

858
00:48:45,922 --> 00:48:47,007
JUST WANTED
TO SAY GOODBYE, CAPTAIN.

859
00:48:47,132 --> 00:48:48,718
HOW'S IT GOING?

860
00:48:48,843 --> 00:48:50,052
