864
00:48:58,018 --> 00:49:00,646
SOUNDS MOST PROMISING.
GOOD LUCK.

865
00:49:01,606 --> 00:49:04,983
HOW OFTEN MANKIND
HAS WISHED FOR A WORLD

866
00:49:05,109 --> 00:49:07,570
